OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThe morning will be overcast
OL,6,Fwith haar, this becoming patchy as the
OL,7,Fday gradually becomes brighter. The
OL,8,Fodd bright spell will be interspersed
OL,9,Fwith the occasional shower.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA few showers will continue
OL,12,Finto the night along with the chance
OL,13,Fof the odd fog patch over Shetland. A
OL,14,Fband of rain will move over Orkney
OL,15,Ftowards the morning.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FCloud and rain over Orkney in
OL,18,Fthe morning will move to Shetland as
OL,19,Fthe rain becomes patchy in the
OL,20,Fafternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
