OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA dry
OL,6,Fand bright morning becoming cloudy
OL,7,FSaturday afternoon. Outbreaks of rain
OL,8,Fspread north overnight, followed by
OL,9,Fshowers Sunday. The showers become
OL,10,Ffrequent during Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
